N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 196.20 - Advertisements

State Regulations

Any educational institution or other organization offering
approved courses may not make or publish any false or misleading statement
regarding employment opportunities which may be available as a result of the
successful completion of a course or acquisition of a
license. Notes
